---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About WPCNA
metaDescription: Learn what WPCNA is and how it helps connect neighborhoods across White Plains.
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>About WPCNA</h1>
    <p>WPCNA connects neighborhood associations and helps residents follow civic life across White Plains.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="about-overview">
      <div class="about-intro">
        <p class="eyebrow">What WPCNA does</p>
        <h2>Neighborhood connection, practical civic information</h2>
        <p>The White Plains Council of Neighborhood Associations brings neighborhood associations together, shares civic information, and helps residents follow citywide issues through a neighborhood lens.</p>
      </div>

      <figure class="about-photo">
        <img src="{{ site.aboutImage | withPrefix }}" alt="{{ site.aboutImageAlt }}" loading="lazy">
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="about-card-grid">
      <article class="about-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Council role</p>
        <h3>Sharing information and encouraging local action</h3>
        <p>WPCNA works to enhance quality of life in White Plains neighborhoods by helping residents, neighborhood associations, and public officials stay connected.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="about-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Using this site</p>
        <h3>Find what residents need quickly</h3>
        <p>Use the site for neighborhood-relevant events, neighborhood profiles, WPCNA agendas, meeting materials, and ways to submit community-serving updates.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="about-support-grid">
      <div class="sidebar-card" id="contact-form">
        <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
        <h3>Get in touch</h3>
        <p>Send questions, corrections, or neighborhood news.</p>
        <form class="contact-form" action="{{ site.contactFormAction }}" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="{{ site.contactFormSubject }}">
          <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">
          <input type="hidden" name="_template" value="table">

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="contact-name">Name</label>
            <input id="contact-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="contact-email">Email</label>
            <input id="contact-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="contact-subject">Subject</label>
            <input id="contact-subject" name="topic" type="text" required>
          </div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="contact-message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit">Send message</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-card about-note-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">How WPCNA works</p>
        <h3>By-laws and committees</h3>
        <p>WPCNA's by-laws and committee work give neighborhood associations a structure for sharing information, tracking issues, and coordinating on citywide topics.</p>
        <p>Use the contact form if you need help finding governance materials or want to ask how the council is organized.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
